SUMMARY:Volunteers Needed for Fairy Trail Day
DESCRIPTION:South Mountain Conservancy Activities Meetup Group\n**[SIGN UP
  GENIUS LINK HERE!](https://www.signupgenius.com/go/10C0849ABAB2CA7F4C61-6
 3036835-2026#/)**\n\nThe **South Mountain Conservancy** is seeking enthusi
 astic volunteers (ages **16+**) to help make our **family-friendly\, fairy
 -filled celebration** a magical success!\n\n🧚 This is a wonderful oppor
 tunity for members of our SMC community to come together and support a bel
 oved event — plus\, it’s a fun way to earn **service hours** while hel
 ping the **South Mountain Conservancy & Fairy Trail**!\n\n**Volunteer Role
 s Available (more on the Sign up Genius!):**\n🏡 Fairy House Making Stat
 ion\n🧾 Merch & Membership Table\n🚦 Traffic Directing (21+)\n🌞 Eve
 nt Greeters\n\nPlease contact Penni Malakates (opdirector@somocon.org) wit
 h any questions!
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/somocon/events/313529831/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260225T220735Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260225T220735Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: South Mountain Conservancy
UID:event_313545916@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260331T030251Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260502T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260502T120000
SUMMARY:Fairy Trail Day 2026
DESCRIPTION:South Mountain Conservancy Activities Meetup Group\n**Join Us 
 for the Fourth Annual Fairy Trail Day!**\n\nThe fairies of the South Mount
 ain Reservation invite you to our **4th Annual Fairy Tales on the Fairy Tr
 ail**! This festival-style event promises a day filled with fun and magic\
 , including: storytelling\, fairy house building\, fairy hair\, a magical 
 scavenger hunt and more!\n\nWings\, crowns\, and t-shirts will be availabl
 e for purchase\, with all proceeds benefiting the South Mountain Reservati
 on Fairy Trail.\n\nDress up in your sparkliest attire\, complete with crow
 ns and wings (or purchase them at the event)\, and let’s celebrate the m
 agic of the Fairy Trail together!\n\nAll proceeds go directly to the SMC F
 airy Trail Fund.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/somocon/events/313545916/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260226T213432Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260226T213432Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE:Meetup: South Mountain Conservancy
UID:event_313635916@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260331T030251Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260516T083000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260516T103000
SUMMARY:SMR Mayapple Trail Runs
DESCRIPTION:South Mountain Conservancy Activities Meetup Group\nRunners ar
 e invited to register for the 17th annual Mayapple Trail Runs to be held o
 n Saturday\, May 16\, 2026 in beautiful South Mountain Reservation in Esse
 x County\, N.J. based out of the Locust Grove Picnic Area\, 197 Glen Avenu
 e\, Millburn.\n\nThe races are organized by the volunteers of the South Mo
 untain Conservancy (SMC) with the support of the Essex County Parks Depart
 ment.\nThe USA Track and Field sanctioned races provide an informal but su
 pportive trail race environment for runners who are up to the challenge of
  completing 5\, 10\, or 20 miles\, or ultra-marathoon distances of 50K (31
  miles) and 50 miles. There is also an informal\, untimed one-mile race fo
 r kids 14 and under. Starting times depend on the race. The 50k and 50 mil
 e races start at 8:30. All proceeds support the mission of the Conservancy
  as a steward and advocate for the park and its public programs.\n\n## Mil
 lburn\, NJ • 50 Miler\, 50K\, 20 Miler\, 10 Miler\, 5 Miler\, Kids 1 Mil
 e Run\n\n**Registration closes: Sat\, May 16 @ 11:59PM ET**\n**To register
  as a runner or volunteer (we need you!) go to [Ultrasignup.](https://ultr
 asignup.com/register.aspx?did=135418) For very detailed descriptions and i
 nformation on group discounts\, go to our MTR [website](https://sites.goog
 le.com/view/south-mtn-mayapple-trail-runs).**\n![](https://s3.amazonaws.co
 m/img.ultrasignup.com/event/banner/ac9f4786-ce56-461c-bb7a-c6dbd288ebf0.jp
 g)[Volunteer ](https://ultrasignup.com/volunteer.aspx?dtid=65285)[Register
 ]()\n\n* [197 Glen Ave](https://www.google.com/maps?q=40.7274458\,-74.3030
 852&z=17&basemap=terrain)\n\n##\n\n*
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/somocon/events/313635916/
